{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>This is event delegation in JavaScript</p>\n<h2>What is event bubbling? Event capture?</h2>\n<p id=\"message\">Here is a message</p>\n<ul id=\"list\">\n  <li>Hi there</li>\n  <li>Hello</li>\n  <li>Hello again</li>\n</ul>\n<script>\n   const messageElement = document.querySelector(\"#message\");\n   document.querySelector('#list')\n     .addEventListener(\"click\", event => messageElement.innerText = event.target.innerText);\n</script>","frontmatter":{"path":"/event-delegation","date":"2018-09-11","title":"What is Event Delegation?"}}},"pageContext":{}}